metadata.name: Eggi
metadata.description:
The Egg is not just an ordinary Egg! Join Eggi NFT, and become the first of its prestigious elite club of owners. 
Eggi is a collection of eggs growing in the beginning of metaverse - a generative collection of unlimited supply of Eggs that live on the Ethereum Blockchain. 
Are we just eggs? This Eggi can be anything. With each purchase of an Eggi, you receive a pass into the metaverse. There are still many surprises to be revealed, and the drop will come faster than you think...Will you be the lucky one?
